Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:21.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様一体 何者だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.51,utaware def,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:26.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,-私は…\N-え… へっ へっひ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:27.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よっ 寄るなっ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:27.68,utaware def,,0,0,0,,D... Don't come near me!
