Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:19:59.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カーッカッカッカッカッカッカッカッ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:03.59,utaware def,,0,0,0,,Why did you do this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:03.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何故こんな真似をするのだっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:06.10,utaware def,,0,0,0,,There you go! That anger...
